
'''= Transparência Hacker (Hacker Transparency) is a group that works with (h)activism in favor of public transparency and open data. Previous and ongoing projects''' 

URL = http://thacker.com.br/


=Description=

"Transparência Hacker ([http://thacker.com.br/ Hacker Transparency]) communityis a group list (with a co-working space in São Paulo - and  online discussion list thackday@googlegroups.com) that works, as its name says, with (h)activism in favor of public transparency and open data. Previous and ongoing projects include [http://otoridades.com.br/ Otoridades], a portal where Brazilians can denunciate abuses of power, and [http://mapaslivres.org/ Mapas Livres], which focuses on open mapping."


